text.section:
The department may collaborate with the United States Department of Agriculture, the University of Kentucky College of Agriculture Cooperative Extension Service, local Area Agencies on Aging, community agencies, foundations, philanthropic organizations, farmers, and local fiscal courts to:
Identify funding sources;
Establish services and a program delivery strategy;
Market the program to citizens and farmers; and
Develop strategies to introduce fresh, locally grown fruits and vegetables into school food programs.
